cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with a computer vision problem of segmenting white matter bundles in diffusion-weighted MRI. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses a deep learning approach, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves image processing and segmentation, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
